snippet.title: Snufkin: Melody of Moominvalley - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the announcement trailer for Snufkin: Melody of Moominvalley to see a peek at the world, characters, and more, in this upcoming musical adventure game. Snufkin: Melody of Moominvalley launches in 2023 on PC and consoles.

In Snufkin: Melody of Moominvalley, use the power of music to bring Moominvalley back to its beautiful origins, after the Park Keeper and his officers have formed hideous parks all over the valley.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #Moomin
